12_SAS_On Cloud Models Characteristics of Hybrid Cloud.


Q1
What is a hybrid cloud?
ANS
A HYBRID CLOUD IS A CLOUD COMPUTING ENVIRONMENT THAT COMBINES THE USE OF BOTH PUBLIC AND PRIVATE CLOUD MODELS WHICH ALLOWS ORGANIZATIONS TO LEVERAGE BENEFITS OF BOTH DEPLOYMENTS. ORGS. CAN INTEGRATE AND MANAGE APPS AND DATA ACROSS BOTH ENVIRONMENTS. IT PROVIDES FLEXIBILITY, SCALABILITY, COST EFFICIENCY, SERVICES OF PUBLIC CLOUDS WHILE ALSO PROVIDING CONTROL, SECURITY, CUSTOMIZATION BY PRIVATE CLOUDS.
Q2
What are some characteristics of hybrid clouds?
ANS
RESOURCE LOCATION
COST & EFFICIENCY
CONTROL
SKILLS
Q3
What are resource locations in hybrid clouds?
ANS
THERE ARE SPECIFIC RESOURCES THAT RUN IN THE PUBLIC CLOUD AND OTHER DEPENDENT RESOURCES THAT RUN IN THE PRIVATE CLOUD.
Q4
What is the cost in hybrid clouds?
ANS
HYBRID CLOUD MODELS ALLOW AN ORG TO LEVERAGE SOME BENEFITS OF COST, EFFICIENCY, SCALE ETC. IN PUBLIC CLOUD MODELS SO YOU CAN TAKE ADVANTAGE OF BOTH PRIVATE AND PUBLIC.
Q5
What is the efficiency in hybrid clouds?
ANS
ABILITY TO OPTIMIZE RESOURCES, COST EFFICIENCY, PERFORMANCE, SCALABILITY AND ELASTICITY, DATA MANAGEMENT AND GOVERNANCE ACROSS BOTH PRIVATE AND PUBLIC CLOUDS. IT ALLOWS FOR THE BEST OF BOTH WORLDS.
Q6
With hybrid clouds an organization can take advantage of both public and private clouds? True/False.
ANS
TRUE
Q7
What is control in hybrid clouds?
ANS
YOUR ORGANIZATION WILL RETAIN MOST OF THE MANAGEMENT CONTROLS BECAUSE YOU ALSO HAVE YOUR INFRASTRUCTURE RUNNING IN THE PRIVATE CLOUD.
Q8
What are skills in hybrid clouds?
ANS
YOUR ORG WILL NEED CONSIDERABLE AMOUNT OF TECHNICAL SKILLS TO BUILD, MANAGE, MAINTAIN THE HYBRID CLOUD ENVIRONMENT.
Q9
With hybrid clouds an organization has to manage infrastructure in a private cloud and integration components with the public cloud must be maintained by the organization's technical team? True/False.
ANS
TRUE
Q10
When it comes to management controls in hybrid cloud an organization doesnâ€™t have much control? True/False.
ANS
FALSE


